Wallace Lupino https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wallace_Lupino 0 Wallace Lupino (23 January 1898 – 11 October 1961) was a British-born stage and film actor who was part of the Lupino family. He appeared in 63 films between 1918 and 1945, most often with his older brother, Lupino Lane. He was born in Edinburgh, Scotland, and died in Ashford, Kent, England.
